<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Bhurborlor is running dangerously low on medicine for the injured.
Collect a pile of alpine seeds.
Collect a clump of mountain herbmoss.
Deliver the alpine seeds, urqobombyx larva, and mountain herbmoss to Bhurborlor.
You there, outsider! I have run dangerously low on ingredients for the concoction of essential medicine. Could I trouble you to go and fetch more?
While our size and strength is far greater than any visitor, there are no few of us that still fear injury and sickness.
I would send you to acquire three things: alpine seeds, an urqobombyx larva, and a good handful of mountain herbmoss. Fortunately, I believe they can all be harvested up the hill north of here.
Journey up the hill to the north and you should be able to find alpine seeds, mountain herbmoss, and at least one urqobombyx larva without much difficulty.
Did you have any trouble finding everything?
I am truly in your debt, outsider. Likewise, my kin will surely rest easy knowing the medicine supply has been replenished.

When Valigarmanda escaped its prison of ice, I confess I feared our doom to be imminent. But not only did you and yours swiftly end its rampage, the puissant healing magicks of your blue-clad companion saved a great many lives.
Rest assured, the ingredients you brought today will be put to good use preparing medicine for those still convalescing. Truly, our people cannot thank you enough!
